Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:44.26,Chn,,0,0,0,,先生,我们特来告诉你，你所保持的世界上最大的屎的纪录 刚被打破了\N{\rEng}Sir, we wish to inform you that your record for biggest crap has just been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:48.41,Chn,,0,0,0,,什么?! 这不可能! 新的纪录有多大?\N{\rEng}What?! That's impossible! How big was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.68,Chn,,0,0,0,,今天我们在这共同为首位获得欧洲人类排泄物协会\N{\rEng}We are here to honor the first American...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:05.03,Chn,,0,0,0,,颁发的世界上最大便便的奖章的美国人表示祝贺！\N{\rEng}to bring home the distinguished EFSM medal for biggest crap ever taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:11.48,Chn,,0,0,0,,嘿 看到了吗, Sharon, 那可是总统大人! 嘿 Sharon!\N{\rEng}Hey look, Sharon, it's the President! Hey Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:17.87,Chn,,0,0,0,,让我们欢迎颁奖嘉宾 欧洲人类排泄物协会的会长 Orloff Broloff先生\N{\rEng}To present the award I give you the dean of the EFSM, Sir Orloff Broloff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:26.71,Chn,,0,0,0,,谢谢，议员先生 在超过一个世纪的时间里, 欧洲人类排泄物协会一直在-\N{\rEng}Thank you, Senator. For over a hundred years, the European Fecal Standards and Meas-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.96,Chn,,0,0,0,,Broloff先生! Broloff先生!\N{\rEng}Herr Broloff! Herr Broloff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:31.74,Chn,,0,0,0,,是真的吗?\N{\rEng}Das shpoitenhoff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,厄...女士们先生们\N{\rEng}Ah ladies and gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:38.46,Chn,,0,0,0,,我们接受到一条最新消息，我们刚接到了一份 来自Bono先生的特制视频声明\N{\rEng}I understand we have just received a special video-taped announcement from Bono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.99,Chn,,0,0,0,,Bono? 酷！\N{\rEng}Bono? Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:44.39,Chn,,0,0,0,,请在大屏幕上播放这段视频?\N{\rEng}Could we play the tape on the big screen, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:48.64,Chn,,0,0,0,,各位好， 我是Bono.\N{\rEng}Hello everyone! I, am Bono.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:02.76,Chn,,0,0,0,,这几年来，为非洲寻求帮助和发展 已经成了我生命中的一部分\N{\rEng}For years it has been my honor to try and bring focus to the needs in Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:05.87,Chn,,0,0,0,,今天，我有一个特别的消息带给大家\N{\rEng}And today, I have very exciting news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:12.22,Chn,,0,0,0,,在昨晚大约8点20分的时候，我拉下了 一坨重达9.5卡里克的便便\N{\rEng}Last night, at twenty past eight, I took a crap weighing nine and a half Courics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.92,Chn,,0,0,0,,Bono?!\N{\rEng}Bono?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:21.05,Chn,,0,0,0,,正如你们所看到的, 这可是一整坨 这是我有史以来拉过的最大一坨\N{\rEng}As you can see, it is one solid piece. It is my biggest crap to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:25.54,Chn,,0,0,0,,我敢发誓它的真实性 谢谢各位，祝上帝保佑你们\N{\rEng}And I swear to its authenticity. Thank you, and God bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:36.45,Chn,,0,0,0,,你们都听见啦，女士们先生们! 目前最大的便便是9.5卡里克!\N{\rEng}You heard it, ladies and gentlemen! The official biggest crap is 9.5 Courics!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:38.97,Chn,,0,0,0,,一起祝贺Bono!\N{\rEng}Congratulations to Bono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:01.71,Chn,,0,0,0,,爸爸，我想晚餐快好了哦\N{\rEng}Dad, I think dinner's almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.55,Chn,,0,0,0,,我差点就成功了\N{\rEng}I almost did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:07.09,Chn,,0,0,0,,我差点就凭自己的本事真正的做点什么\N{\rEng}I almost made something of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:12.61,Chn,,0,0,0,,你知道吗，当你那么接近成功的时候，你甚至 会觉得，或许你的生活将走向不凡\N{\rEng}You know, when you get real close, you start to think that maybe your life is gonna matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:18.98,Chn,,0,0,0,,我意思是，这可是我真正的心血结晶啊\N{\rEng}I mean, this was something I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:23.73,Chn,,0,0,0,,从我身体里分离出来的，也是我身体的一部分啊\N{\rEng}Something that came from me! That was a a part of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:27.38,Chn,,0,0,0,,我这辈子做的唯一有意义的事情！\N{\rEng}The only thing I ever made that was any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.13,Chn,,0,0,0,,天啊，别想那么多了，老爸 - 谢谢你\N{\rEng}Gee, thanks a lot, Dad. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.33,Chn,,0,0,0,,我只是...\N{\rEng}And I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:40.32,Chn,,0,0,0,,我知道在我以后的日子里，我可能再也 不会有如此这么接近成功的机会了\N{\rEng}I know that this late in my life I'll never come so close to finally having meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.52,Chn,,0,0,0,,来吧，两位，烤宽面条已经做好了\N{\rEng}Come on guys, lasagna's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.43,Chn,,0,0,0,,宽面条做好了\N{\rEng}Oh. Lasagna's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:52.22,Chn,,0,0,0,,你听见了吗， Stan? 你妈说宽面条已经做好了!\N{\rEng}You hear that, Stan? Mom says lasagna is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:55.43,Chn,,0,0,0,,我能听出你的讽刺意味, Sharon!\N{\rEng}I can see through your sarcasm, Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:58.89,Chn,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊? - 你完全可以说, Sharon!\N{\rEng}What are you talking about? - You can say it, Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.44,Chn,,0,0,0,,我知道Bono比我好!\N{\rEng}I know Bono's better than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:03.88,Chn,,0,0,0,,很遗憾我不是Bono，满意了吧?!\N{\rEng}I'm sorry I'm not Bono, all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:07.99,Chn,,0,0,0,,真对不起，我没有上亿的资产， 也没有诺贝尔奖提名！\N{\rEng}Sorry that I don't have billions of dollars and a Nobel prize nomination!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:12.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,Randy, 这真荒谬! - 哦，这可是我的真心话, Sharon!\N{\rEng}Randy, this is ridiculous! - Oh, that's real mature, Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:16.09,Chn,,0,0,0,,你就像什么事情都在搞笑一样! 这整件事对你来说就是个大笑话，是不是?!\N{\rEng}Just act like everything's funny! It's a big joke to you, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:19.85,Chn,,0,0,0,,就是一个笑话! 不要碰我!\N{\rEng}Just a big joke! Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:25.81,Chn,,0,0,0,,你能相信吗?! 这一切都只是为了谁拉的屎大！\N{\rEng}Can you believe him?! All this over what guy took the biggest crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:29.12,Chn,,0,0,0,,你不理解的, Mom. 你真的不理解\N{\rEng}You don't understand, Mom. You just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.29,Chn,,0,0,0,,Wha? Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:44.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,他们怎么能只凭那个叫Bono寄来的一张照片就让他获胜?\N{\rEng}How come they just let that Bono guy send a picture of his crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:48.63,Chn,,0,0,0,,因为他是Bono, 这就是原因. -但是他可能伪造照片啊，这不公平!\N{\rEng}Because he's Bono, that's why. - But he could have faked it. It isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:52.71,Chn,,0,0,0,,已经没办法了，他现在已经是记录保持者了，我啥都干不了\N{\rEng}Doesn't matter. He's got the record now, there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:57.52,Chn,,0,0,0,,哦，有件事你能做的!你可以再拉一次! - 什么?\N{\rEng}Oh yes there is! You could do it again! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:12:01.76,Chn,,0,0,0,,你想，上次你甚至连要拉最大的屎这个念头都没有\N{\rEng}Think about it. You weren't even trying to take the biggest crap last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.50,Chn,,0,0,0,,想想你如果马力全开的话！\N{\rEng}Imagine if you actually worked at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.85,Chn,,0,0,0,,嘿，没错！\N{\rEng}Hey. Hey that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:10.70,Chn,,0,0,0,,不，我不能再经历一次了，实在太痛苦了\N{\rEng}No. I can't go through all that again. It's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:14.60,Chn,,0,0,0,,加油, Randy. 我打赌你可以轻松再拉坨那么大的屎!\N{\rEng}Come on, Randy. I'll bet you can crap that big again easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.62,Chn,,0,0,0,,加上正确的食谱和锻炼，你拉出的便便绝对没有极限！\N{\rEng}With the right diet and training, who knows what you're capable of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:23.37,Chn,,0,0,0,,伙计们, 算了吧! 结束了! 那只是一次巧合! 我再也不能拉出那么大的便便了\N{\rEng}Guys, forget it! It's over! It was a fluke crap, I'll never take one that big again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:27.54,Chn,,0,0,0,,结束了吗, Randy?! 我们可是都亲眼看过你那坨大便便的啊!\N{\rEng}Is it over, Randy?! We all saw that crap you took!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:33.07,Chn,,0,0,0,,这绝不只是巧合! 这是你身上的某种潜能，使你 创造了奇迹!\N{\rEng}That was no fluke! There's something inside you that made you able to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:37.97,Chn,,0,0,0,,Randy, 你是有天赋的! 谁知道上帝为什么要给你这个天赋，但是他确实是给了！\N{\rEng}Randy, you have a gift. Now who knows why God chose you, but he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:42.56,Chn,,0,0,0,,如果你就这么放弃的话，你一辈子也不会知道...\N{\rEng}And if you walk away now, you'll always wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.27,Chn,,0,0,0,,你能拉多大的便便\N{\rEng}how big a crap you could have taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:51.08,Chn,,0,0,0,,我可能需要很多的帮助 - 我们一切都乐意效劳！\N{\rEng}I would need a lot of help. - That's what we're here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:53.23,Chn,,0,0,0,,好吧, Randy, 你准备怎么办?!\N{\rEng}Come on, Randy, what do you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.63,Chn,,0,0,0,,我想说...\N{\rEng}I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.36,Chn,,0,0,0,,让Bono知道我的厉害!\N{\rEng}Let's give Bono a run for his money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:09.50,Chn,,0,0,0,,这里是CNN头条新闻.\N{\rEng}This is CNN Headline News.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,今晚，一场关于伊朗的军事打击...\N{\rEng}Tonight, a possible attack on Iran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:15.55,Chn,,0,0,0,,可能意味着新的中东战争拉开序幕\N{\rEng}may mean the beginning of a new war in the Middle East.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:16.94,Chn,,0,0,0,,欧，不是吧\N{\rEng}Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:22.21,Chn,,0,0,0,,但是首先要说的是，世界上最大便便的纪录是不是 又会再次被破呢?\N{\rEng}But first, the record for the world's biggest crap, will it again be broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:26.48,Chn,,0,0,0,,科罗拉多的Randy Marsh为了挑战新的纪录 已经准备了三周的时间了\N{\rEng}Randy Marsh of Colorado is now three weeks into his quest to make a new crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:30.28,Chn,,0,0,0,,他把所有的日常时间都用于在P.F. Chang吃东西\N{\rEng}Spending nearly every waking hour at P.F. Chang's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.78,Chn,,0,0,0,,这有什么新闻价值吗？\N{\rEng}Is this really newsworthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.24,Chn,,0,0,0,,你根本就不了解\N{\rEng}You just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.11,Chn,,0,0,0,,是的，我不能理解\N{\rEng}You're right. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:40.78,Chn,,0,0,0,,同时, 一些人在质疑Bono纪录的真实性\N{\rEng}At the same time, some people are questioning Bono's current record entry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:43.59,Chn,,0,0,0,,因为没有人亲眼看到那坨便便\N{\rEng}saying nobody has ever seen it in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:47.91,Chn,,0,0,0,,目前暂时联系不到Bono,因为他现在正在非洲\N{\rEng}Bono could not be reached for comment, as he is currently in Africa helping the needy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:57.24,Chn,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello.\N{\rEng}Hello, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:02.05,Chn,,0,0,0,,Marsh 正在准备打破那个纪录 我们想你应该知道这件事\N{\rEng}Marsh is attempting to break the record again. We thought you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:06.69,Chn,,0,0,0,,他不可能击败我的9.5卡里克! - 他决定试试\N{\rEng}He can't beat my nine and a half Courics! - Well he's going to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:11.21,Chn,,0,0,0,,可以，但他必须在你面前拉下这泡屎！ 在苏黎世！\N{\rEng}Fine, but he has to take the crap in front of you! In Zurich.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.01,Chn,,0,0,0,,Bono, 我们以前从来没有这项规矩\N{\rEng}Bono, we've never had that rule before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:16.23,Chn,,0,0,0,,这是唯一知道他没有作弊的办法！\N{\rEng}I's the only way you can know he's not cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.71,Chn,,0,0,0,,如果他不是在苏黎世拉的话，那就不能算！\N{\rEng}If he doesn't crap in Zurich, it shouldn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.98,Chn,,0,0,0,,超声检查是很简单的, Mr. Marsh.\N{\rEng}Ultrasound is very simple, Mr. Marsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.22,Chn,,0,0,0,,我们将用无害的超声波检查你的胃\N{\rEng}We're going to use harmless waves to look inside your belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:29.29,Chn,,0,0,0,,首先要在你的肚子上涂点防护油\N{\rEng}Just gonna put some warm gel on your stomach first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.64,Chn,,0,0,0,,Ok, 深呼吸\N{\rEng}Okay, take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:38.53,Chn,,0,0,0,,我看见一坨屎了，我不能保证 但是我想它可能有\N{\rEng}I see the crap now. I can't say for sure, but I, I'd say is about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:41.52,Chn,,0,0,0,,14卡里克 -14?!\N{\rEng}14 Courics. - Fourteen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.02,Chn,,0,0,0,,太棒了，Randy! - 我能看看嘛?\N{\rEng}That's great, Randy! - Can I, Can I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:49.77,Chn,,0,0,0,,可以 这是你的盲肠，这里是你肚子里的那坨屎\N{\rEng}Sure. This is your colon and here is the feces growing inside your belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.81,Chn,,0,0,0,,伙计们，我们有个问题!\N{\rEng}Guys, we have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:09.89,Chn,,0,0,0,,刚和欧洲便便协会通过话 他们说Randy 必须去苏黎世拉这坨屎\N{\rEng}I talked to the EFSM and they say Randy has to take the crap in Zurich.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.04,Chn,,0,0,0,,苏黎世？\N{\rEng}In Zurich?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.87,Chn,,0,0,0,,他们说这是Bono要求的 他们也没办法\N{\rEng}They say that Bono is demanding it and that their hands are tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:18.33,Chn,,0,0,0,,对不起 Mr. Marsh, 以你目前的身体状况 坐飞机是非常不合适的\N{\rEng}I'm sorry Mr. Marsh, I I cannot condone you traveling on an airplane in your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.74,Chn,,0,0,0,,在你粪便成型期，出行是非常不安全的\N{\rEng}It is never safe to fly during your turd trimester.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:33.54,Chn,,0,0,0,,Hi, 请问我能和Mr. Bono说几句话吗? - Mr. Bono, 您有位年轻的拜访者!\N{\rEng}Hi, could I speak to Mr. Bono, please? - Mr. Bono, you have a young gentleman caller!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.91,Chn,,0,0,0,,把喷气机准备好, Bovis! 我要走了\N{\rEng}Get the jet ready, Bovis! I've got to be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:45.51,Chn,,0,0,0,,Hi, 我的名字叫Stan Marsh 我父亲正向您的最大便便纪录发起挑战\N{\rEng}Hi, my name is Stan Marsh. My dad's trying to beat your record for biggest crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.55,Chn,,0,0,0,,哦，对的，他赶不到苏黎世了，是吗？\N{\rEng}Oh right. He can't make it to Zurich, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:52.48,Chn,,0,0,0,,这就是我到这里来的原因 这个最大便便的纪录，对你很重要吗？\N{\rEng}That's kind of what I'm here for. Do you really need the biggest crap record?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:56.09,Chn,,0,0,0,,请问您能稍微退让一下，让我爸爸获得这个头衔吗?\N{\rEng}Could you maybe see your way to just letting my dad have this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:59.36,Chn,,0,0,0,,让他获得? 为什么我要这么做?!\N{\rEng}Let him have it? Why would I do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:04.37,Chn,,0,0,0,,先生，您得理解我们，我老爸 以前从来没赢过任何东西..\N{\rEng}Look, you gotta understand, sir. My dad's never won an award for anything. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.45,Chn,,0,0,0,,他从来就没有赢过任何一个奖项和奖杯\N{\rEng}He doesn't have one single trophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:11.41,Chn,,0,0,0,,甚至我都有个销售体育画报第二名的奖杯\N{\rEng}I mean, even I have a second-place trophy for most Sports Illustrated subscriptions sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:14.01,Chn,,0,0,0,,那是因为我拿了第一名\N{\rEng}I have the first-place trophy for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.39,Chn,,0,0,0,,伙计，难道你还不满足吗? 我意思是..\N{\rEng}Dude, don't you have enough? I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:21.21,Chn,,0,0,0,,你有数不清的钱, 喷气式飞机，世界上最大的乐队 一个超性感的老婆\N{\rEng}you got tons of money, a jet and the biggest rock band in the world, a hot wife and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:25.96,Chn,,0,0,0,,你甚至被授予了爵位.. 我意思是，在某些地方，你就不能让一让吗？\N{\rEng}you've been knighted. I mean, at some point, can't you just kind of fuck off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:29.58,Chn,,0,0,0,,我要让大家都知道我的价值，我有多重要\N{\rEng}I want people to know that I'm worth something. That I matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:33.69,Chn,,0,0,0,,我只是要求仅在这么一件事上， 您可以让我爸爸当一次第一名\N{\rEng}All I'm asking is that maybe with this one thing, let my dad be number 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.82,Chn,,0,0,0,,你仍然可以当第二名啊\N{\rEng}And you can still be number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:39.98,Chn,,0,0,0,,第二名?! 第二名?!\N{\rEng}Number two?! Number two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.38,Chn,,0,0,0,,谁都不能这么说我!\N{\rEng}Nobody calls me that anymore and gets away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:47.37,Chn,,0,0,0,,把这话收回去! 把它收回去! - 我收回!\N{\rEng}Take it back! Take it back! - I take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.93,Chn,,0,0,0,,说我不是第二名! - 你不是第二名!\N{\rEng}Say I'm not number two! - You're not number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:52.48,Chn,,0,0,0,,这还差不多，我才不是呢！\N{\rEng}That's right! I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.13,Chn,,0,0,0,,这家伙有什么病?\N{\rEng}What is wrong with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:02.88,Chn,,0,0,0,,你爸爸现在有危险，跟我来\N{\rEng}Your father is in grave danger. Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.47,Chn,,0,0,0,,这坨便便一定超大啊\N{\rEng}It must be quite a crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.65,Chn,,0,0,0,,加油, Randy，你必须使劲!\N{\rEng}Come on, Randy. You have to push!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:33.35,Chn,,0,0,0,,你在说什么?! 你怎么知道我爸爸会处于危险之中?!\N{\rEng}What are you saying?! How do you know my dad is gonna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:36.56,Chn,,0,0,0,,因为从没有人能拉这么大的屎\N{\rEng}Because nobody has ever taken a crap that big before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.62,Chn,,0,0,0,,那就是说Bono的新纪录确实是个谎言!\N{\rEng}So Bono's newest record is a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:43.71,Chn,,0,0,0,,我最初发现事情不对劲的时候，是我发现了 Bono的首个最大便便的奖杯\N{\rEng}Look, I first knew something was wrong when I looked at Bono's first award for biggest crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:47.07,Chn,,0,0,0,,上面写着1960年颁发的奖杯 - 所以呢?\N{\rEng}It said he took it in 1960. - So?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:51.94,Chn,,0,0,0,,那一年Bono刚刚出生 然后我什么都明白了\N{\rEng}So that's the year Bono was born. Then it all made sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:56.86,Chn,,0,0,0,,为什么Bono能这么有才, 如此有爱心 可看上去依然和一坨屎没什么分别?\N{\rEng}How could Bono be so talented, so caring and yet seem like such a piece of crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:03.26,Chn,,0,0,0,,因为他本来就是一坨屎 你明白了吗? Bono根本不是什么纪录保持者\N{\rEng}Because he is crap. Don't you get it? Bono is not the record holder...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:07.54,Chn,,0,0,0,,他自己就是那个纪录 - 没错\N{\rEng}He's the record. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:15.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,我做不到! 我做不到!\N{\rEng}I can't do it! I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:19.74,Chn,,0,0,0,,这坨屎实在是太大了, Mr. Marsh. 我们必须剖开肚子把它取出来!\N{\rEng}The crap is simply too big, Mr. Marsh. We must perform a Caesarean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:22.94,Chn,,0,0,0,,可那样的话，还能算数吗? - 不算!\N{\rEng}But then, does it still count? - Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:27.69,Chn,,0,0,0,,最大的屎必须是你拉出来的! - 他说的没错\N{\rEng}A biggest crap means you crapped it out! - I believe that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:32.08,Chn,,0,0,0,,很遗憾, Mr. Marsh, 但是如果不是你亲自拉出来的话\N{\rEng}We are sorry, Mr. Marsh, but if you cannot crap out the crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.26,Chn,,0,0,0,,那就不能算数\N{\rEng}it's not really a crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:37.84,Chn,,0,0,0,,No... No.\N{\rEng}No... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:41.74,Chn,,0,0,0,,没事的，Randy. 你已经尽了最大努力了\N{\rEng}There there Randy. You gave it your best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:45.23,Chn,,0,0,0,,我想见我的太太  Sharon? Sharon?\N{\rEng}I want my wife. Sharon? Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:48.97,Chn,,0,0,0,,什么?! - 对不起, Sharon.\N{\rEng}What?! - I'm sorry, Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:53.89,Chn,,0,0,0,,对不起让你失望了 对不起我没能赢Bono\N{\rEng}I'm sorry that I let you down. I'm sorry I can't crap like Bono.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:58.59,Chn,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了, Bono, 看来你的纪录依旧保持\N{\rEng}Well congratulations, Bono, it appears your record is intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:02.10,Chn,,0,0,0,,我早就知道是这样 - 等等！停一下！\N{\rEng}I had a feeling it would be. - Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:06.89,Chn,,0,0,0,,爸爸，你以前那坨屎就应该赢了！ Bono从来没有拉过能赢你的那坨！\N{\rEng}Dad, your old crap counts. Bono never took a second crap to beat yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:10.58,Chn,,0,0,0,,把他赶出去！ - 你在说什么，年轻人?\N{\rEng}Get him out of here! - What are you talking about, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:16.33,Chn,,0,0,0,,某人有个秘密，Bono从来就不是这个纪录的 保持者! 他就是那坨屎!\N{\rEng}Somebody's been keeping it a secret. Bono was never the record holder! He's the record!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:21.17,Chn,,0,0,0,,这不是真的! 杀了这个小孩! 我要他死!\N{\rEng}It's not true! Kill the kid! I want him dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:25.79,Chn,,0,0,0,,太晚了, Bono. 这个小男孩已经知道了真相\N{\rEng}It's too late, Bono. The boy has learned the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:30.69,Chn,,0,0,0,,Broloff会长, 你关于这个知道什么? - 我恐怕那是真的\N{\rEng}Herr Broloff, what do you know of this? - It's true, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:36.30,Chn,,0,0,0,,直到Mr. Marsh出现前， 我才是世上最大便便纪录的保持者\N{\rEng}You see, until Mr. Marsh came along, I was the record holder for the biggest crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:41.29,Chn,,0,0,0,,我在1960年拉的 那是我有生以来拉的最神奇的一坨屎\N{\rEng}I took it back in 1960. It was the most amazing crap I'd ever taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:44.46,Chn,,0,0,0,,不，爸爸，别再说了！\N{\rEng}Poppa no! Say nothing more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:47.90,Chn,,0,0,0,,过来吧，我亲爱的孩子\N{\rEng}Come to me, my darling precious child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:56.67,Chn,,0,0,0,,当我获得纪录后，我把那坨便便 带回了家\N{\rEng}After I had broken the record I took the crap home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:20:02.13,Chn,,0,0,0,,我是如此的为它自豪，我决定留下它， 像照顾我自己的孩子一样照料它\N{\rEng}I was so proud of it that I decided to keep it, to try and raise it like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:06.87,Chn,,0,0,0,,不要说了，爸爸，不要说了 - 这就是了，我亲爱的小便便\N{\rEng}No Poppa. No Poppa. - There there, my little crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:10.78,Chn,,0,0,0,,别哭了 这儿，想吸奶奶吗？\N{\rEng}Don't cry. Here, do you want the biddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:13.81,Chn,,0,0,0,,Does Bono want the biddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.18,Chn,,0,0,0,,是的，他爱吸奶奶，不是吗?\N{\rEng}Yes, he likes the biddy doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.08,Chn,,0,0,0,,我晕\N{\rEng}Dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:23.99,Chn,,0,0,0,,我把那坨屎放在办公室，给它营养 给它喂奶\N{\rEng}I kept the crap in my office, nursed it, fed it biddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:27.71,Chn,,0,0,0,,很快，它吸着奶奶长壮了，长大了!\N{\rEng}And soon biddy made him strong. Biddy made him grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:32.77,Chn,,0,0,0,,甚至成为了我们这个时代最有影响力的人物之一 轻点，Bono，那会弄疼了我的奶奶\N{\rEng}Into one of the most influential figures of our time.Easy Bono, that hurts the biddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.63,Chn,,0,0,0,,奶奶\N{\rEng}Biddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.53,Chn,,0,0,0,,我的小便便完成了很多精彩的壮举\N{\rEng}My little crap has accomplished many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:42.98,Chn,,0,0,0,,但是他从来不能接受他自己其实是便便的事实 （美国俚语中，numer two有便便的意思）\N{\rEng}But he could never shed the fact that he was really a number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:46.94,Chn,,0,0,0,,所以他用他一生的时间和精力要当第一名， 在所有事情上\N{\rEng}So he spent his life trying to be number one, in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:50.26,Chn,,0,0,0,,这就是他为什么在能完成那么多的事， 帮助那么多人后，\N{\rEng}That's why he's able to do so much, try to help so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.76,Chn,,0,0,0,,可让人觉得依然不过是一坨屎\N{\rEng}but still seem like such a piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.86,Chn,,0,0,0,,你的行为让我们神圣的协会有了污点，Broloff会长\N{\rEng}You have blemished this noble society's good name, Herr Broloff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:59.53,Chn,,0,0,0,,我有吗?! 瞧瞧我当年拉的这坨屎！\N{\rEng}Have I?! Look at the crap I took all those years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:03.74,Chn,,0,0,0,,Bono现在已经有6英尺高，重达80卡里克!\N{\rEng}Bono is now almost six feet tall and over 80 Courics in weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:07.76,Chn,,0,0,0,,无论你们怎么看，它依旧是记录!\N{\rEng}No matter how you look at it, he is still the record!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:11.19,Chn,,0,0,0,,欧，上帝啊，来了! 疼啊 疼 疼 疼 疼!\N{\rEng}Oh God, here it comes! Oh, hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:14.45,Chn,,0,0,0,,疼 疼 疼 疼 疼 疼!\N{\rEng}Hot, hot, hot, hot, hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:24.98,Chn,,0,0,0,,我的上帝啊... - 这一定超过了100卡里克!\N{\rEng}My God... - It must be over a hundred Courics!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:27.74,Chn,,0,0,0,,爸爸，你还好吗？ - 恩\N{\rEng}Dad, are you all right? - Yeah, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:30.63,Chn,,0,0,0,,我很好! 感觉好多了\N{\rEng}No, I'm good! Feel a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:34.44,Chn,,0,0,0,,Mr. Marsh, 非常抱歉 如果你不介意的话\N{\rEng}Mr. Marsh, we apologize and if it's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:38.91,Chn,,0,0,0,,请拿好早就应该属于你的奖杯\N{\rEng}we would like to present you... your long overdue trophy.